{"tid":1184630,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲近期有去沙巴","createTime":"2019-06-03T18:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T05:01:15.000Z","uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e608d644b8160eb7d368640f7c317830607a85e0","tid":1184630,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T18:28:21.000Z","msg":"第一次自由行2條友乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以好多野想問。<br />\n咁我plan左應該去四日，自己想潛水<br />\n我想問巴打們去國家公園體驗潛水會去到先join local tour定上網報？我見上網報有識講廣東話既教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有冇試過連續兩日報呢啲體驗潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他團係咪其實都好易行行下報到？ 咁其實冇咩野可以係出發前做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後就係貴重物品點樣跟身，2條友落水一定冇人睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5248a95884a2ef0f169ecd41e39eae2160378ad","tid":1184630,"uid":163489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完沙巴番黎 但係就無潛水 不過去個邊報Local tour就平好多 報左280港幣 去美人魚島加睇螢火蟲"},{"pid":"77dc2e487a67eba58c43293f014a921b8f2f096a","tid":1184630,"uid":139995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5248a95884a2ef0f169ecd41e39eae2160378ad","tid":1184630,"uid":163489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完沙巴番黎 但係就無潛水 不過去個邊報Local tour就平好多 報左280港幣 去美人魚島加睇螢火蟲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T18:37:05.000Z","msg":"係邊度報local tour？"},{"pid":"bdeb0690c1a9b106ba9748e2681c76e19509131b","tid":1184630,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"可以一早報定，去到報都得可能平一百幾十，網上報就格下價先<br />\n其實睇你時間夠唔夠去到先報，如果你搭下午機去到都夜晚想第2日即刻去玩就網上報定<br />\n<br />\n你報啲tour都有人幫你睇住啲嘢，基本上唔洗擔心"},{"pid":"08df29683ab2e2fcc28f8826a9f300f079632c0e","tid":1184630,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0